          "mod": "2026-06-06T22:22:59.145",
          "lines": [
            0,
            57,
            120
          ],
          "text": "The recalculate() code in NetMismatch is also relatively slow, because it doesn’t do a very smart job of creating a map between cschem nodes and cpcb nodes. ",
